          "description": "Update: April 7. What happened to the old team up front? The patient service here is terrible now! You can tell they don\u2019t care to service you! They want you to scan the QR code and stay out their face! Awful, I will not be returning\n\nEverytime  I come in I am delighted by my experience! The front desk I want to give a warm shout out to the woman who was there today. She was very kind and patient with my mother and I despite it being our first visit for her. We\u2019ve never had initial care like that. The doctor and the medical assistant that assisted us were splendid you think you wouldn\u2019t receive top care at an urgent care but here is where it is at!! I will definitely be coming back to this location if any of my family members feel sick.",
