          "description": "I have visited City MD on various occasions and find it very professional and satisfying. Most recently I was treated by Alyssa and the PA, Mithani. They did the appropriate tests and blood work. The test results were later posted in the Summit App. I was given a clear understanding and assessment of my situation. I\u2019m happy to have this clinic in the area where I live.",
