          "description": "People are great, but they switched to a \u201cmake everyone wait outside in line\u201d instead of \u201ccheck in and we will text you when to come back\u201d because from a business perspective they feared it was bringing business down. Now you have dozens and dozens of sick people waiting down the block in 40 degree winter weather, instead of giving people the option of waiting at home till their time a slot. Healthcare in America.",
