          "description": "So mean reception , came in with a hot water burn hand and doesn\u2019t give a shit. I didn\u2019t  know how to do appointment and  told me scan a stupid QR code and nothing. So terrible",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xoRE5qaEJaM3B2T0V4ZlpUQklXQzF0Y1VsR1FtYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x31f7491ebbf8773b!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOlhDNjhBZ3pvOExfZTBIWC1tcUlGQmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
